sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Commit History Webview
participant Router as HistoryMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GetCommitDetailsUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository implements GitHistoryOperations
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Select commit
App->>Router: history/commitDetailsRequest(repositoryLocator, commitHash, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, commitHash, signal)
UseCase->>Repo: getCommitDetails(commitHash, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: getCommitDetails(executionContext, commitHash, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitDetails(executionContext, commitHash, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: GitCommit details and file changes
Runtime-->>Repo: GitCommit details and file changes
Repo-->>UseCase: GitCommit details and file changes
UseCase-->>Router: CommitDetails
Router-->>App: history/commitDetailsResponse(requestId, details)
App-->>User: Render message and changed files
